    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">At 3rd level, as long as the gunslinger has at least 1 grit point, she gains the following benefits. First, she gains a +2 bonus on </span><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: url('ui/cursors/pointer.webp'), pointer; font-size: 13px;\" href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Initiative\">initiative</a><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;checks. Furthermore, if she has the&nbsp;</span><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: url('ui/cursors/pointer.webp'), pointer; font-size: 13px;\" href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/combat-feats/quick-draw-combat\">Quick Draw</a><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;feat, her hands are free and unrestrained, and the firearm is not hidden, she can draw a single firearm as part of the&nbsp;</span><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: url('ui/cursors/pointer.webp'), pointer; font-size: 13px;\" href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Initiative\">initiative</a><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\"> check.</span></p>"
    },
